- name: Build host list
  set_fact:
    host_list: "{{ groups['iris:birdseye'] | join('\n') }}"
  run_once: true

- name: Mail the Patching schedules to respective teams
  mail:
    to: "{{ EMAIL_RECEIPTS }}"
    cc: "{{ EMAIL_CC_RECEIPTS }}"
    subject: "Monthly Patching Schedule for {{ GROUP_NAME }} servers - {{ PATCH_MONTH_BKP }} {{ PATCH_YEAR }}"
    body: "{{ lookup('template', 'templates/mail_body.j2') }}"
  delegate_to: localhost
  run_once: true

Hi Team,

Please find the {{ PATCH_MONTH_BKP }} month patching schedule for {{ GROUP_NAME }} servers.

Kindly create a change record and send it to supporting application team.

Non-Production Servers schedule 3rd Tuesday of every month || {{ NONPROD_PATCH_SCHEDULE }}
Production Servers schedule 3rd Thursday of every month    || {{ PROD_PATCH_SCHEDULE }}

Below {{ GROUP_NAME }} servers will be patched:

{{ host_list }}
